+
'''Forever the Sickest Kids''' is an American pop band from [[North Richland Hills, Texas]], who are currently signed to [[The Universal Motown/Universal Republic Group|Universal Motown Records Group]]. In issue 228 of ''[[Alternative Press (music magazine)|Alternative Press]]'', the group was named the number one underground band in the "22 Best Underground Bands". Their first EP, ''[[Television Off, Party On (EP)|Television Off, Party On]]'', was released on July 3, 2007. Their debut album, ''[[Underdog Alma Mater]]'', was later released on April 29, 2008. The first part of their new three-part [[mini-LP]] (a collection entitled 3P), ''[[The Weekend: Friday]]'', was released on November 17, 2009, with their newest, self-titled album released on March 1, 2011.
